# DevProfile Analyzer - Frontend Environment Configuration

## Backend API Configuration

# Backend API URL (development)
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

# Backend API URL (production - update when deployed)
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend.railway.app/api

## Feature Flags

# Use backend API instead of direct GitHub API calls
VITE_USE_BACKEND=true

## App Settings
VITE_APP_NAME=DevProfile Analyzer

## GitHub API (Optional - only if not using backend)
# VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_personal_access_token
